# Reliability Runtime V1

Minimal starter for a recording + replay system focused on FastAPI applications.

## Install

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # Linux/macOS
# or .venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1 on Windows PowerShell

pip install -e .
